1. Can you speak English?
2. Did you ask anybody for help?
3. Did it snow much last winter?
4. What are you cooking for dinner?
5. Why do you have to get up early in the morning?
6. Can you help me in the evening?
7. Is there any butter in the fridge?
8. Where are you going in the evening?
9. Is there any jam in the jar?
10. Do you want to drink mineral water?
11. What will you have, fish or meat?
12. Will you bake a cake in the evening?
13. Do you like to smoke after lunch?
14. Are you reading the new book?
15. Were you allowed to watch TV at night when you were a child?
